Bilazea template is a PHP/HTML/CSS/AJAX template used in several sites
- PHP core
- HTML/CSS/AJAX presentation

It's currently an 'on working' project, a prototype (version 0.1)
First official beta release will be available next year, in January 2011, as version 0.2
First official release will be available in 2011, no precise date for now, as version 1.0


Main demonstration can be seen on Bilazea.com, on page http://bilazea.com/Bilazea-template


It is a very simple framework designed to create quickly a website
- Main language used is PHP, to create navigation stuff mainly
- MOOTOOLS (http://github.com/mootools/mootools-core), XHTML and CSS are used to present content
